                     <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18250519-119-off708 t18250519-119-crimeloc710"></join>, a pair of breeches, value 1 l.; two waistcoats, value 1 l.; two handkerchiefs, value 7 s., and a pair of boots, value 1 l., the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18250519-119-victim678" type="victimName">
                        Thomas 
                        Knight
                     <interp inst="t18250519-119-victim678" type="surname" value="Knight"></interp>
