                     </persName>
                  ; five waistcoats, value 1 l.; two handkerchiefs, value 7 s.; a pair of trowsers, value 2 s.; two aprons, value 2 s., and a metal chain, value 6 d., the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18250519-119-victim679" type="victimName">
                        John 
                        Wilkes
                     <interp inst="t18250519-119-victim679" type="surname" value="Wilkes"></interp>
